On 30 September, at the sixth meeting of the Standing Committee of the 13th People ' s Congress of Fujian Province of China (journalist Ryong Min), the General Assembly adopted the Regulation on the Promotion of Ecological Civilization in Fujian Province.
For the first time ever, Green Water and Green Mountain is written into Fujian Province legislation, which is operational and enforceable throughout the regulations.
Fujian is China ' s first ecological civilization pilot zone.
According to the Head of the Legal Department of the People ' s Government of Fujian Province, it is necessary and urgent to develop a comprehensive and holistic basic code for the construction of an ecological civilization that addresses the issue of decentralized regulations and regulations, policy documents regulating the construction of an ecological civilization and providing the legal basis for the development of regulations, normative documents and measures.
This regulation, which fully reflects the Fukuan character, transforms mature experience in ecological civilization-building practices into legal forms of application: In the case of the replicable and replicable “Hingting experience” of the Fujian soil conservation management process, the regulations provide that local people's governments at the county level and above shall strengthen their unified leadership of soil and water conservation, and define priority areas for soil erosion prevention and management, based on the results of the soil erosion survey; and in the case of the river longing system in Fujian province, the regulations raise the length of rivers and lakes to the legislative level, stipulating that the people's governments at the local level should fully implement river and lake longing systems, and implement river and lake pipelines, responsibilities and funding.
The regulation provides for a life-long system of accountability for ecological damage.
The leading leadership cadres and the relevant officials, who are responsible for leadership, will be held accountable for their lives, in contravention of the requirements of scientific development, causing serious damage to ecological resources.
It was explained that the Ordinance on the Promotion of the Construction of Eco-Civilization in Fujian Province will be implemented on 1 November this year.
